861
00:41:45,210 --> 00:41:46,210
Thanks.

862
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:49,290
What?

863
00:41:49,291 --> 00:41:50,689
Salad's healthy.

864
00:41:50,690 --> 00:41:53,289
