01:21:27,337 --> 01:21:28,803
- What's in that frame?

1590
01:21:31,740 --> 01:21:33,093
- Photo of his wife.

1591
01:21:36,760 --> 01:21:39,128
- Now agent, Whitmeyer,
will you tell the jury

1592
01:21:39,129 --> 01:21:42,679
